  "name": "Whip Like Strikes",
  "type": "spell",
  "_id": "DiElHNTWbUZV3M7s",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Icons/Bukijutsu.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>By levying the weight and tension brought on by the chain and the weapon your mastery over the flail allows you to change and react to the weapons path by flicking your wrist and altering its course in a dozen micro movements.</p><p>This Jutsu cannot score a critical hit. Select a creature within range and make 5 Melee Taijutsu attacks against them as your weapon strikes many times in the blink of an eye. Each hit deals your [weapons damage] + 1d6, depending on how many hits, the creature suffers varying effects.</p><p>• [1 Strike]: The Creature loses 15 feet of movement for 1 minute</p><p>• [2 Strikes]: All previous effects, and a rank of bruised for 1 minute</p><p>• [3 Strikes]: All previous effects, The target loses 2 AC for 1 minute</p><p>• [4 Strikes]: All previous effects, The target gains a ranked of Staggered for 1 minute</p><p>• [5 Strikes]: All previous effects, The target gains 5 ranks of concussed for 1 minute</p>",
